This paper is about face alignment using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a novel approach using a single deep network, which is a technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses data augmentation and training skills, which are relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
